column15: Number multiplied to Sioux' "Raw" evaluation in order to get -1.
This number multiplied by Raw Eval of each county yields Sioux-Constant Output
Sioux-Constant Output*4 if Sioux-Constant Output is below 0
This was done in order to make the blue counties not all look so light blue.
The exact number, 4, can be lowered or raised if disired.
